{"tid":2018191,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾迪臣：美斯無世界盃不如我 C.朗就是得力量","createTime":"2020-05-15T12:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T05:18:50.000Z","uid":34571,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"196acddbf3a5db935fcf65f99d0d93f0f952bbe1","tid":2018191,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"巴西2002年世界盃冠軍成員艾迪臣（Edilson）稱，美斯（Lionel Messi）和C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）都不如他。<br />\n<br />\n  48歲的艾迪臣對巴西電視媒體說：「我巔峰時比尼馬踢得好，他需要贏得世界盃才能比我強。」<br />\n<br />\n  「對美斯來說，要想比我更好，他也需要先拿到世界盃。」<br />\n<br />\n  「C.朗拿度只是力量強，雙腳射門很好，但我比他技術更好。」<br />\n<br />\n  2002年韓日世界盃，艾迪臣是巴西隊的一員，4強對土耳其時正選出戰，對英格蘭的8強後備上陣，小組賽對哥斯達黎加和中國都出過場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/05/15/4/4d42b8062be90dc960c4dd9b9bdd270d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F05%2F15%2F4%2F4d42b8062be90dc960c4dd9b9bdd270d.jpg&h=e337ed64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b5f4502dcee47eded38a8510c0673eee942d2da","tid":2018191,"uid":18520,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"邊撚個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53c27cdb895f6ff70a4ca5e2dc3788b616847ef","tid":2018191,"uid":43328,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"法國球星基沙文認為自己有資格跟C朗拿度及美斯爭奪個人獎項，因為自己已跟對方屬同一水平。"},{"pid":"cf93af09794de7ccfea03a3a2281e1721aab1d8e","tid":2018191,"uid":282509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6b5f4502dcee47eded38a8510c0673eee942d2da","tid":2018191,"uid":18520,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"邊撚個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif